EN: She is a pure and kind girl.

ZH: 这家公司主打的是纯天然的产品。
EN: This company specializes in pure natural products.

ZH: 这幅画展现了他对纯美的追求。
EN: This painting reflects his pursuit of pure beauty.

ZH: 森林里有一条纯净清澈的小溪。
EN: There is a pure and clear stream in the forest.

ZH: 纯黑色的礼服给她增添了一丝神秘感。
EN: The all-black dress added a touch of mystery to her.

ZH: 这种纯正的风格在当时广受好评。
EN: This pure style received great acclaim at the time.

ZH: 这眼镜镜片是纯钛金属制成的。
EN: The lenses of these glasses are made of pure titanium.

ZH: 他的动机是纯粹的，没有任何企图。
EN: His motives are pure, without any ulterior motives.

ZH: 这个决定是出于你的纯情感情吗？
EN: Was this decision made out of your pure emotions?

