EN: That country has the purest natural environment in the world.

ZH: 这种原料的纯质量很难得到。
EN: It is difficult to obtain the pure quality of this material.

ZH: 在这个企业，纯利润占了大部分收入。
EN: In this company, pure profit accounts for most of the income.

ZH: 他坚持要选择纯正的原料来制作健康食品。
EN: He insists on using pure ingredients to make healthy food.
